@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vndhsv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.88 / v1 + 0.44) / tmp) * wp.sin((tmp + 0.67 - v2 + 0.85)))
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.57 - v0 + 0.28) / 0.24) + ((tmp + 0.04 * v0 + 0.28) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.22)))
    v2 = (v2 / v1)
    v1 = v0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((tmp + 0.46 - v2 + 0.13)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v2 + 0.26 / v2 + 0.46)))
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
